AethOS Pro / Enterprise — commercial license (reference)
=========================================================

Proprietary features (advanced planning, self-healing extensions packaged separately,
enterprise gates, etc.) are **not** licensed under the open-source terms that apply to this
repository’s default distribution.

Commercial customers receive a separate agreement covering:

- permitted use, seats, and deployment scope  
- support and SLA (if purchased)  
- termination and audit (as applicable)

**Contact:** use your commercial contact channel (e.g. ``license@aethos.ai`` or your contract
manager). This file is **not** a binding contract — it only documents where terms live.
